ill whatever, and build whatever. I'm hooked.Overall the game score does not really matter as its not a complete game. But you will get a experience that you won't in any other  incomplete game. It is also more complete than many games in early access. The game has been in development for a long time, but the number of work that can be done to the game is a list no one wants to deal with. But even with a long development I think this is one of the few games that will get the love it deserves. And I love playing the game. This game will be in my library for a few years.8.5/10WIll sacrifice towns again just to figure out that there was something easy that could have been done to save the town."
